Package: glyexp
Title: Glycoproteomics and Glycomics Experiments
Version: 0.15.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Bin", "Fu", , "23110220018@m.fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8567-2997"))
Description: Provides 'SummarizedExperiment'-based containers for glycomics and
    glycoproteomics experimental data. 'GlycomicSE' and 'GlycoproteomicSE'
    validate glycan-specific annotations while retaining standard assay,
    'rowData', 'colData', and metadata interfaces. The legacy 'experiment()'
    API remains available with lifecycle deprecation warnings to support a
    staged migration of the 'glycoverse' ecosystem.
